data.description: ***BUY THIS HOME AND I'LL BUY YOURS*** ****3.99% FIXED FOR 30 YEARS CONVENTIONAL LOAN AVAILABLE******Step into the main floor of this remarkable home where spaciousness and charm converge. As you enter you are greeted by distinct areas that cater to every aspect of modern living including a cozy living room with a fireplace, a spacious area for dinning room and another separate area that could be ideal for home office. The kitchen is a culinary heaven, featuring it's own fireplace that adds a touch of comfort. Equipped with stainless steel appliances and adorned with stone countertops and a breakfast area beacons for casual dining boasting a balcony with beautiful view for special gatherings. On the second floor you can find the master suite that boasts an elegant master bathroom complete with a deep soaking tub, a separate modern shower and a convenient double vanity. You will find two more stylish designed bathrooms on second floor and three remaining generous bedrooms provide ample space for comfort and relaxation. Descend into the full finished basement, here a spacious family/gaming room awaits perfect to create lasting memories with family and friends. And as you step outside you'll discover a spacious backyard that offers endless possibilities, whether it's for outdoor gatherings, gardening or simply enjoying the fresh air.
